title: Jubilees Of Zion
description: I hate to say that Jubilees of Zion is the weakest of Midnite&#039;s first 3 albums, because people might infer that it is a poor set, but that is far from the truth.  In fact, this is an excellent album that maintains the group&#039;s rich sound.   It&#039;s just that the songs aren&#039;t quite as consistently classic as they are on Ras Mek Peace and Unpolished (but they&#039;re damn close)
